dataStudio.name: Data Studio Meta Data from OmniIndex
dataStudio.description: Unstructured Data Meta analysis. (https://omniindex/io/datastudio). This connector allows you to create dashboards within Google Data Studio from your unstructured Data. To use this Connector, your organization must have an available OmniIndex Platform instance, or be signed up with our free SaaS version. Please contact our support team, if you have any questions.
dataStudio.shortDescription: Unstructured Data Meta Analysis within the OmniIndex Platform.
